<p>While listening to the podcast, I realised that I'd been mentioned 4 times on them and I never actually knew! So, as you can imagine this was a really exciting moment for me when I realised.</p>
<p>One of the podcast episodes mentioned a feature that I contributed to the Laravel framework that allows you to add extra default validation rules (PR: <a href="https://github.com/laravel/framework/pull/40137">#40137</a>):</p>
